---
title: Seared Chicken & Parsley Brown Butter Sauce with Potato Mash & Steamed Veggies
description: Nostalgia is the secret ingredient here. Steamed veggies and buttery, mash, it’s a homestyle meal that warms you up
from the inside. The superstar of this dish is the seasoned chicken cooked in garlic and herbs. Sit down and enjoy this
meal with family and friends or your own wonderful company!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
